headline: Rachel Reeves’ plan could bring tourist tax to English hotels and Airbnb’s
summary: In the upcoming budget, the chancellor plans to let mayors in England introduce a local tourist tax on overnight stays in hotels, guest houses and Airbnb-style rentals.
